    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine, showroom condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, a masterclass in atmospheric induction featuring individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a linear power band to an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed via a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is flawless, with documented subframe reinforcement and proactive rod bearing replacement already performed. Every suspension bushing remains tight, ensuring the sharp turn-in and torsional rigidity this platform is renowned for. Finished in its original factory coating with zero paint correction required, this is a mechanically sorted, high-revving icon for the discerning collector.",
