    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional 2018 Porsche Cayman in showroom condition. This single-owner vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen inclement weather. The Jet Black Metallic paint is absolutely flawless, having been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating and paint protection film (PPF) on the entire front clip; there are no stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks to be found. The interior is equally pristine, featuring Agate Grey leather that remains supple with no visible wear on the bolsters or touchpoints. Every electronic component, from the premium Bose surround sound system to the PCM navigation, operates exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, this car is perfect. It boasts a comprehensive service history exclusively performed by Porsche factory-trained technicians, with a complete binder of receipts and a stamped maintenance booklet included. The tires are fresh, the wheels are free of any curb rash, and the undercarriage is spotless. This is a rare find for a discerning enthusiast who demands a vehicle with no excuses and a transparent history. Includes two keys, original window sticker, and a custom-fit indoor car cover.",
